org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="bd899d0d-e747-4e88-bab3-3f93a5d75b42" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="242">下記は、参考URLの情報をもとに <strong data-start="17" data-end="45">株式会社イーライフ［リースキン師勝中央店］様向け</strong>に差し替えた版です。会社名・所在地・電話番号・設立日などは公開情報を反映しています。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 71px;"><a href="https://www.indirect.jp/e-life/company.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.indirect.jp/e-life/company.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 71px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">株式会社INDIRECT - 名古屋　グラフィックデザイン・店舗デザイン</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span><br data-start="124" data-end="127">
サービス内容は、清掃用具リース、建物・店舗・住居・特殊清掃、カーペット・厨房・水まわり・トイレ・照明・床・エアコン清掃などの公開情報を参考に構成しています。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 105px;"><a href="https://www.indirect.jp/e-life/product3.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.indirect.jp/e-life/product3.html?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 105px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">株式会社INDIRECT - 名古屋　グラフィックデザイン・店舗デザイン</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<p data-start="244" data-end="295">GitHub Pages 用なので、下記を <strong data-start="266" data-end="282"><code data-start="268" data-end="280">index.html</code></strong> として保存してください。</p>
