そのまま <strong data-start="169" data-end="185"><code data-start="171" data-end="183">index.html</code></strong> に置き換えて使えます。</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="199" data-end="61806"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1" style=""><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style=""><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="h-full border border-transparent"><div class="h-full w-full"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="inline-flex"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost py-2 text-sm font-medium size-9 rounded-full px-2 hover:bg-token-bg-secondary" aria-label="コード ファイルをダウンロードする" type="button" aria-disabled="false"><div class="flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#1a3695" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="編集する"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="ビューを切り替える" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-tertiary dark:bg-gray-900"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: translateX(calc(100% + 2px));"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="コード" aria-pressed="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="プレビュー" aria-pressed="true" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="group pointer-events-auto overflow-hidden corner-superellipse/1.1 shadow-elevation-01 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-900 flex w-full aspect-video w-full relative"><div class="h-full w-full"><div class="relative flex h-full w-full"><div class="bg-token-main-surface-primary absolute inset-0 m-auto origin-center overflow-hidden pointer-events-auto" style="transform: none; opacity: 1;"><iframe title="プレビュー" class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden" allow="midi" src="./oni_files/saved_resource(5).html" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-forms" tabindex="0"></iframe></div></div></div><span class="absolute end-2 top-2 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-secondary shadow-elevation-01 rounded-full border-0" aria-label="フル スクリーン"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#03424d" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="61808" data-end="61829">必要なら次にすぐできます。<br data-start="61821" data-end="61824">
たとえば：</p>
<ol data-start="61831" data-end="61988">
<li data-section-id="1baefh2" data-start="61831" data-end="61854">
<p data-start="61834" data-end="61854"><strong data-start="61834" data-end="61852">鬼イラストをもっと大きくする</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f96f7d" data-start="61855" data-end="61881">
<p data-start="61858" data-end="61881"><strong data-start="61858" data-end="61879">鬼をヘッダーやフッターにも配置する</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cw6luv" data-start="61882" data-end="61917">
<p data-start="61885" data-end="61917"><strong data-start="61885" data-end="61915">「社内用」ボタンを目立たなく/もっと目立つようにする</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1998zcm" data-start="61918" data-end="61953">
<p data-start="61921" data-end="61953"><strong data-start="61921" data-end="61951">実際の写真を入れる前提で画像差し替えしやすい形にする</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="otlx8e" data-start="61954" data-end="61988">
<p data-start="61957" data-end="61988"><strong data-start="61957" data-end="61988">メールフォーム（Formspree など）対応版にする</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="61990" data-end="62042" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">必要なら次は<br data-start="61996" data-end="61999">
<strong data-start="61999" data-end="62033">「鬼をもう少しe-lifeっぽい雰囲気に寄せた別バージョン」</strong><br data-start="62033" data-end="62036">
を出します。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="応答アクション" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="回答をコピーする" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="その他のアクション" type="button" id="radix-_r_1kt_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) h