x h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼo">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"oni-card"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"label"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><span>オリジナル鬼モチーフ</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"oni-svg-wrap"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;svg</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"oni-svg"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">viewBox</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"0 0 160 160"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">xmlns</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">role</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"img"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">aria-label</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"鬼モチーフのオリジナルイラスト"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>      ...</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/svg&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>※ 元イラストの複製ではなく、サイト用のオリジナル鬼イラストです。</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/div&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="993" data-end="1011">を、下記に丸ごと置き換えてください。</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1013" data-end="1267"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="コピーする" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="編集する"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use h