em"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"#services"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-icon"</span>&gt;🏠&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;住居清掃&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;ハウスクリーニング&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">a</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-item"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"#services"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-icon"</span>&gt;❄️&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;エアコン&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;清掃・メンテナンス&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">a</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-item"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"#services"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-icon"</span>&gt;🚿&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;水まわり&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;厨房・浴室・トイレ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">a</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-item"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"#services"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-nav-icon"</span>&gt;✨&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;特殊清掃&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;通常清掃で難しい汚れ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">small</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section worries"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worries"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Worries&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;こんなお困りごとはありませんか？&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;オフィス・店舗・住居の「きれい」を維持するには、日々の清掃だけでなく、用具の管理や定期的なプロ清掃が大切です。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-grid"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-icon"</span>&gt;🧼&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;清掃用具の管理に手間がかかる&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;マットやモップを自社で購入・洗浄・交換するのは意外と負担です。リースなら清潔な状態を保ちやすく、管理の手間を軽減できます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-icon"</span>&gt;🏬&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;店舗や事務所の印象を良くしたい&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;入口・床・トイレ・照明まわりなどは、お客様や従業員の印象に直結します。定期的な清掃で清潔感のある空間づくりを支えます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"worry-icon"</span>&gt;🧽&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;普段の掃除では落ちない汚れがある&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;厨房の油汚れ、カーペットの汚れ、水まわりの黒ずみ、エアコン内部など、専用の道具と技術が必要な清掃にも対応します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section services"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"services"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Service&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;イーライフの提供サービス&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;清掃用具のリースから、建物・店舗・住居・特殊清掃まで。お客様の環境に合わせて、必要な清掃サービスを組み合わせてご提案します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-grid"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-mat"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;清掃用品&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;マット・モップ・清掃用具リース&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;オフィスや店舗の入口・床まわりを清潔に保つためのマット、モップ、清掃用具をご提案します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;玄関マット・フロアマット&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;モップ・清掃道具のリース&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;衛生的な交換・管理をサポート&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-office"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;法人向け&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;店舗・オフィス清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;事務所、店舗、施設の床・トイレ・照明・共用部などを清掃し、快適な事業環境を整えます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;床清掃・ワックス対応&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;トイレ・洗面まわり清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;照明・共用部の清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-house"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;個人向け&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;住居・ハウスクリーニング&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;ご家庭の気になる汚れをプロの手で丁寧に清掃。普段のお掃除では届きにくい場所もお任せください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;キッチン・浴室・トイレ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;窓・サッシ・床まわり&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;入退去前後の清掃相談&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-aircon"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;快適空間&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;エアコン清掃・メンテナンス&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;エアコン内部のホコリや汚れ、ニオイの原因にアプローチ。店舗・事務所・住居の空調管理におすすめです。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;エアコン内部の汚れ対策&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;ニオイ・カビの原因を清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;定期的なメンテナンス相談&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-water"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;水まわり&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;厨房・浴室・トイレ清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;厨房の油汚れ、水アカ、黒ずみ、トイレの汚れなど、衛生面で気になる場所を丁寧に清掃します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;厨房・レンジまわり清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;浴室・洗面・トイレ清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;水アカ・カビ・油汚れ対策&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-thumb thumb-special"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"label"</span>&gt;専門対応&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;カーペット・特殊清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;カーペットや通常清掃では対応が難しい汚れなど、現場の状況に合わせて清掃方法をご提案します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"service-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;カーペット清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;建物・店舗・住居の特殊清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;現場状況に応じた清掃提案&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section reasons"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reasons"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Reason&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;イーライフが選ばれる理由&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;清掃用品のリースとプロ清掃の両面から、建物や住まいの「きれい」を継続的に支えます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-layout"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-visual"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-mini-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">strong</span>&gt;Since 2000&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">strong</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;地域に根ざした清掃サービス&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-item"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-number"</span>&gt;01&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;清掃用品から現場清掃まで一括相談&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;マット・モップなどの日常的な清掃用品と、定期清掃・専門清掃をまとめて相談できます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-item"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-number"</span>&gt;02&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;店舗・事務所・住居まで幅広く対応&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;法人の清潔な職場づくりから、ご家庭のハウスクリーニングまで、用途や規模に合わせた清掃サービスをご提案します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-item"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"reason-number"</span>&gt;03&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;現場に合わせた丁寧な提案&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;汚れの種類、素材、使用頻度、清掃の目的を確認し、必要な作業内容を分かりやすくご案内します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section comparison"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"comparison"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Comparison&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;こんな方におすすめです&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;単発の清掃だけでなく、日常的な清潔維持まで考えたい方に向いています。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"comparison-box"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">table</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"comparison-table"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">tbody</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;店舗・オフィスの方&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;入口マットや床、トイレ、照明、共用部など、&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"highlight"</span>&gt;お客様や従業員の印象に関わる場所&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;を清潔に保ちたい場合におすすめです。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;住居の清掃を頼みたい方&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;キッチン、浴室、トイレ、窓、床など、&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"highlight"</span>&gt;普段のお掃除では落としきれない汚れ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;をプロに任せたい場合におすすめです。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;清掃用具も見直したい方&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;マットやモップの購入・洗浄・交換管理を見直し、&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"highlight"</span>&gt;リースで衛生的に運用したい&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;場合におすすめです。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;汚れがひどくて困っている方&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">th</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;厨房の油汚れ、カーペット汚れ、水まわりの黒ずみ、エアコン内部など、専門的な清掃が必要な場合もご相談ください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">td</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">tr</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">tbody</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">table</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section works"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"works"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Operation Example&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;対応例&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;実際の写真は差し替え前提です。現場写真や作業前後の写真を入れると信頼感が高まります。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"works-grid"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-image work-01"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;店舗・事務所の定期清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;床、入口、共用部、トイレなどを清掃し、来店者・従業員にとって気持ちの良い空間を維持します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-image work-02"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;厨房・水まわり清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;厨房の油汚れ、シンクまわり、トイレや洗面など、衛生管理が重要な場所を丁寧に清掃します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-image work-03"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"work-body"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;エアコン清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;店舗・事務所・住居のエアコン内部にたまった汚れやニオイの原因を清掃します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section flow"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Flow&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;ご相談からサービス開始までの流れ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;清掃用具のリースも、現場清掃も、まずはお困りごとをお聞かせください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-grid"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-icon"</span>&gt;📞&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;お問い合わせ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;お電話またはメールで、清掃したい場所・ご希望内容・対応エリアをお知らせください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-icon"</span>&gt;🔍&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;内容確認・現場確認&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;必要に応じて現場の状況を確認し、汚れの状態や必要な清掃範囲を整理します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-icon"</span>&gt;📝&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;ご提案・お見積り&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;清掃内容、リース内容、作業頻度、料金の目安を分かりやすくご案内します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">article</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"flow-icon"</span>&gt;✨&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;サービス開始&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;ご納得いただいた内容で、清掃用品の設置・交換や現場清掃を実施します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">article</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section company"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;Company&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;会社概要&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;北名古屋市を拠点に、地域の店舗・事務所・住まいの「きれい」を支えています。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-layout"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">aside</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-card"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;清潔で、快適で、&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">br</span>&gt;安心できる空間づくりを。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;株式会社イーライフは、リースキン師勝中央店として、清掃用品のリースと各種清掃サービスを通じて、お客様の環境づくりをサポートします。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-contact-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;📍 北名古屋市井瀬木五反地68-3&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;☎ 0568-25-7071&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;🧹 建物・店舗・住居・特殊清掃まで対応&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">aside</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dl</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-table"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-row"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;会社名&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;株式会社イーライフ［リースキン師勝中央店］&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-row"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;所在地&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;〒481-0014 愛知県北名古屋市井瀬木五反地68-3&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-row"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;代表番号&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;TEL. 0568-25-7071&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-row"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;設立&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;2000年4月1日&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"company-row"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;事業内容&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dt</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;マット・モップ・清掃用具のリース、店舗・事務所清掃、住居清掃、カーペット清掃、厨房・水まわり清掃、トイレ清掃、照明清掃、床清掃、エアコン清掃・メンテナンス、特殊清掃&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dd</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">dl</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section faq"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"faq"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-head"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">span</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-kicker"</span>&gt;FAQ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">span</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-title"</span>&gt;よくある質問&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"section-desc"</span>&gt;お問い合わせ前に気になりやすい内容をまとめました。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"faq-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;法人だけでなく、個人宅の清掃も相談できますか？&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;はい、店舗・事務所などの法人向け清掃だけでなく、住居のハウスクリーニングもご相談いただけます。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;マットやモップのリースだけでも依頼できますか？&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;はい、清掃用具のリースのみのご相談も可能です。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;店舗やオフィスの定期清掃はできますか？&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;はい、店舗・事務所・施設などの清掃もご相談ください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;エアコン清掃や水まわり清掃も依頼できますか？&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">summary</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;はい、エアコン清掃・メンテナンス、厨房、水まわり、トイレなどの清掃にも対応しています。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">details</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">    &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">section</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">id</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"container"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact-layout"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;清掃用品のリースも、&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">br</span>&gt;プロの清掃もお気軽にご相談ください。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;店舗・事務所・住居の清掃、マット・モップのリース、エアコンや水まわりの清掃まで、お困りごとに合わせてご案内します。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact-actions"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">a</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"btn btn-secondary"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"tel:0568257071"</span>&gt;0568-25-7071 に電話&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">a</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"btn btn-outline"</span> <span class="ͼ1q">href</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"mailto:info@example.com?subject=ホームページからのお問い合わせ"</span>&gt;メールで問い合わせ&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact-panel"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;ご相談時にお伝えいただきたいこと&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">h3</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact-panel-list"</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;✅ 清掃したい場所、または導入したい清掃用品&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;✅ 店舗・事務所・住居など建物の種類&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;✅ 汚れの状態や気になる箇所&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;✅ 希望時期、作業可能な曜日・時間帯&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;✅ 駐車スペースや搬入経路の有無&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">li</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">ul</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="ͼ1m">div</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span>=<span class="ͼ1o">"contact-note"</span>&gt;※ GitHub Pages単体ではフォーム送信処理ができないため、このサンプルでは電話・メール導線にしています。&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">section</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">  &lt;/<span class="ͼ1m">main</span>&gt;</div><div class="cm-line">  &lt;<span class="ͼ1m">footer</span> <span class="ͼ1q">class</span